'''托马斯·乔纳森·奥索夫'''（{{lang-en|Thomas Jonathan Ossoff}}，{{IPAc-en|'|ɒ|s|ɒ|f}} {{Respell|OSS|off}}，{{bd|1987年|2月16日||}}）<ref name=":6">{{Cite web|title=Thomas Jonathan OSSOFF|url=https://find-and-update.company-information.service.gov.uk/officers/NCeBMyUe53m78PmQf2mR3Jt5Z8A/appointments|accessdate=2020-12-18|work=find-and-update.company-information.service.gov.uk|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512045725/https://find-and-update.company-information.service.gov.uk/officers/NCeBMyUe53m78PmQf2mR3Jt5Z8A/appointments}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Jon Ossoff|url=https://www.jewishpoliticalguide.com/senators/jon-ossoff/|accessdate=2020-12-18|work=[[American_Jewish_Congress|American Jewish Congress]]|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206010300/https://www.jewishpoliticalguide.com/senators/jon-ossoff/}}</ref>，[[美國|美國]][[美國民主黨|民主黨]]籍[[政治人物|政治人物]]、[[紀錄片|纪录片]][[电影制片人|制作人]]和[[调查报导|调查记者]]<ref name="AJC 2020">{{Cite news|url=https://www.ajc.com/blog/politics/georgia-senate-ossoff-nets-another-ends-quarter-with-hand/xR53pjf70RyulxACa30UEL/|title=Georgia Senate: Ossoff nets another $1M, ends quarter with $1.8M on hand|author=Bluestein|first=Greg|date=2020-04-15|work=The Atlanta-Journal Constitution|accessdate=2020-04-17|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112194623/https://www.ajc.com/blog/politics/georgia-senate-ossoff-nets-another-ends-quarter-with-hand/xR53pjf70RyulxACa30UEL/}}</ref>，現任[[喬治亞州|喬治亞州]][[美国参议院|聯邦参议员]]。

奥索夫是[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]提名的2020年[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]]美国参议员选举候选人，与共和党当时在任参议员[[大衛·珀杜|大卫·珀杜]]竞争。<ref name=":9">{{Cite news|author=Fausset|first=Richard|author2=Epstein|first2=Reid J.|date=2020-06-10|title=Jon Ossoff Wins Democratic Senate Primary in Georgia|language=en-US|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/10/us/politics/jon-ossoff-georgia-senate.html|accessdate=2020-06-11|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117133640/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/10/us/politics/jon-ossoff-georgia-senate.html}}</ref>在11月3日的大选中，两位候选人都没有达到50%票数的门槛，引发了2021年1月5日的第二轮选举。<ref name="ajc11052020"/>

2021年1月5日佐治亞州第二輪選舉，奧索夫成功擊敗[[大衛·珀杜|大卫·珀杜]]取得參議員換屆職位，成為117屆國會最年輕的參議員。他也是佐治亚州第一位[[美国犹太人|犹太裔]]参议员，[[美國深南部|美國深南部]]第二位犹太裔参议员。他的胜选令民主黨重新控制參議院。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Warnock Makes History and Democrats Gain Senate Majority|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/politics/politics-news/georgia-runoff-results-1109665/|accessdate=2021-01-26|date=2021-01-06|last=Stuart|first=Tessa|work=Rolling Stone|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211206172313/https://www.rollingstone.com/politics/politics-news/georgia-runoff-results-1109665/}}</ref>

== 早年生活和教育 ==
奥索夫生于[[亚特兰大|佐治亚]]州[[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]的一个[[犹太人|犹太]]家庭，在一个没有[[非建制地區|建制]]的[[非建制地區|社区]]北湖（Northlake）长大。<ref name="electjon.com">{{Cite press release|accessdate=2017-02-21|title=Jon Ossoff Announces Congressional Bid in Georgia|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222084607/https://electjon.com/news/2017/1/4/jon-ossoff-announces-congressional-bid-in-georgia|archivedate=2017-02-22}}</ref>他高中就读于亚特兰大一所[[独立学校|私立]]的帕伊德亚高中。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/can-this-democrat-win-the-georgia-sixth|title=Can This Democrat Win the Georgia Sixth?|author=Bethea|first=Charles|date=2017-03-03|work=[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]|accessdate=2017-03-08|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105170229/https://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/can-this-democrat-win-the-georgia-sixth}}</ref>在高中期间，他在[[公民权利和政治权利|民权]]领袖和美国众议员[[約翰·路易斯_(喬治亞州政治人物)|约翰·刘易斯]]下实习。 

2009年，奥索夫从[[乔治城大学|乔治敦大学]][[埃德蒙·A·沃尔什外事学院|外交学院]]毕业，获得了[[理學學士|理学]][[学士学位|学士学位]]。他选择了由[[美国国务卿列表|美国]]前[[美国国务卿列表|国务卿]][[马德琳·奥尔布赖特|玛德琳·奥尔布赖特]]和[[以色列駐美國大使列表|以色列]]前[[以色列駐美國大使列表|驻美国大使]]迈克尔·奥伦（Michael Oren）所教授的课程。<ref name="wp-2017-02-23">{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/powerpost/paloma/daily-202/2017/02/23/daily-202-will-anti-trump-backlash-let-democrats-win-the-georgia-special-election-to-replace-tom-price/58ae458be9b69b1406c75ceb/|title=The Daily 202: Will anti-Trump backlash let Democrats win the Georgia special election to replace Tom Price?|author=Hohmann|first=James|date=2017-02-23|work=The Washington Post|accessdate=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105170228/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/powerpost/paloma/daily-202/2017/02/23/daily-202-will-anti-trump-backlash-let-democrats-win-the-georgia-special-election-to-replace-tom-price/58ae458be9b69b1406c75ceb/}}</ref><ref name="db-2017-03-01">{{Cite news|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/could-the-resistance-start-with-georgias-special-election|title=Could The Resistance Start With Georgia's Special Election?|author=Murphy|first=Patricia|date=2017-02-27|work=The Daily Beast|accessdate=2017-03-01|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216223529/https://www.thedailybeast.com/could-the-resistance-start-with-georgias-special-election}}</ref>2013年，奥索夫获得了[[倫敦政治經濟學院|伦敦经济学院]][[理學碩士|理学]][[硕士学位|硕士学位]]。

== 新闻调查记者 ==
自2013年以来，奥索夫一直担任Insight TWI（一家常驻[[伦敦|伦敦]]的调查类电视节目制作公司）的常务董事[[首席执行官|兼首席执行官]]，该公司与记者经常合作制关于外国腐败情形的纪录片。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Wilkins|first=Emily|title=Georgia Democrats See Another Opportunity in Race Against Perdue|url=https://about.bgov.com/news/georgia-democrats-see-another-opportunity-in-race-against-perdue/|accessdate=2020-06-30|publisher=Bloomberg Government|date=2020-06-25|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107102829/https://about.bgov.com/news/georgia-democrats-see-another-opportunity-in-race-against-perdue/}}</ref><ref name="Variety">{{Cite news|url=https://variety.com/2020/politics/news/jon-ossoff-senate-georgia-1203522791/|title=Doc Producer Jon Ossoff on His Run for a U.S. Senate Seat in Georgia|author=Ravindran|first=Manori|date=2020-03-05|work=Variety|accessdate=2020-04-17|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105170229/https://variety.com/2020/politics/news/jon-ossoff-senate-georgia-1203522791/}}</ref>该公司制作了[[英国广播公司|BBC]]有关[[东非|东非]][[伊斯兰国|ISIS]][[战争罪|战争罪行]]和死刑队的节目。他还参与制作了关于[[塞拉利昂|塞拉利昂]]戏剧演出的纪录片。 

== 政治生涯 ==

=== 国会工作人员 ===
奥索夫担任国家安全员工和美国众议员汉克·约翰逊（Hank Johnson）的助手长达五年。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.politifact.com/factchecks/2017/apr/03/jon-ossoff/jon-ossoff-national-security-background/|first=Louis|author=Jacobson|date=2017-04-03|title=How extensive was Jon Ossoff's national security background?|work=politifact.com|accessdate=2017-04-06|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108123341/https://www.politifact.com/factchecks/2017/apr/03/jon-ossoff/jon-ossoff-national-security-background/}}</ref>他曾持有绝密权限长达五个月。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/326800-democrats-go-for-broke-in-race-for-tom-prices-seat|title=Democrats go for broke in race for Tom Price's seat|author=Weaver|first=Dustin|date=2017-04-01|work=TheHill|accessdate=2017-04-06|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105170234/https://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/326800-democrats-go-for-broke-in-race-for-tom-prices-seat}}</ref>他于2012年离开了约翰逊的办公室，以获取[[倫敦政治經濟學院|伦敦经济学院的硕士学位]]。<ref>{{Cite news|first=Ashley|author=Lutz|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/jon-ossoff-bio-democrat-georgia-special-election-2017-6|work=Business Insider|date=2012-06-20|title=Meet Jon Ossoff, the 30-year-old who suddenly became one of the most talked-about politicians in America|accessdate=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108004129/https://www.businessinsider.com/jon-ossoff-bio-democrat-georgia-special-election-2017-6}}</ref>在为约翰逊工作之前，他曾在美国众议员和民权领袖[[約翰·路易斯_(喬治亞州政治人物)|约翰·刘易斯]]处担任实习生，刘易斯后来向约翰逊推荐了他。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ossoff aims to connect John Lewis legacy with a new generation|url=https://georgiarecorder.com/2020/12/21/ossoff-aims-to-connect-john-lewis-legacy-with-a-new-generation/|date=2020-12-22|access-date=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106012626/https://georgiarecorder.com/2020/12/21/ossoff-aims-to-connect-john-lewis-legacy-with-a-new-generation/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Georgia US Senate race: Ossoff again campaigning in overtime|url=https://www.clickorlando.com/news/politics/2020/12/23/georgia-us-senate-race-ossoff-again-campaigning-in-overtime/|author=Press|date=2020-12-23|first=Ben Nadler And Russ Bynum, Associated|work=WKMG|access-date=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210105170240/https://www.clickorlando.com/news/politics/2020/12/23/georgia-us-senate-race-ossoff-again-campaigning-in-overtime/}}</ref>

=== 2017年特别选举 ===
