ps://www.ajc.com/news/state--regional-govt--politics/how-impeachment-already-reshaping-georgia-politics/gLxcCv78jxG9AENIGoBTvM/|archivedate=2020-12-21|accessdate=2020-08-21|work=[[Atlanta_Journal_Constitution|Atlanta Journal Constitution]]|date=2019-10-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>同样，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》观察称他2017年的竞选活动与全国民主党相比相距甚远。<ref name="sharper">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/08/us/politics/georgia-special-election-ossoff-handel.html|title=Takeaways From the Georgia Special Election Debate: A Sharper Clash|author=Burns|first=Alexander|date=2017-06-08|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2017-06-13|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108045419/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/08/us/politics/georgia-special-election-ossoff-handel.html}}</ref>

