=== 特朗普政府 ===
奥索夫对[[唐納·川普|唐纳德·特朗普]]总统持严厉批评态度，他批评特朗普“对政府的分裂主义态度” <ref>{{Cite news|first=Cristiano|author=Lima|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2017/04/georgia-ossoff-special-election-237307|title=Georgia Democrat rebuffs Trump: 'I don't have great personal admiration' for him|work=[[Politico|Politico]]|date=2017-04-17|accessdate=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210625014940/https://www.politico.com/story/2017/04/georgia-ossoff-special-election-237307}}</ref>并说：“我非常尊重总统一职。但我并不钦佩总统本人。” <ref name=":3">{{Cite news|url=http://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/329242-george-dem-on-trump-i-dont-have-great-personal-admiration-for|title=Georgia Dem Ossoff: 'I don't have great personal admiration' for Trump|author=Greenwood|first=Max|work=[[The_Hill_(newspaper)|The Hill]]|date=2017-04-18|accessdate=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210625112120/https://thehill.com/blogs/blog-briefing-room/news/329242-george-dem-on-trump-i-dont-have-great-personal-admiration-for}}</ref>特朗普在4月19日初选的前一天发了一条[[Twitter|推文]]，称奥索夫是“极左（Super Liberal）民主党人”，他想“保护罪犯，允许[[非法移民|非法移民]]并提高税收”，奥索夫反驳了特朗普的主张，称他“受了误导”（Misinformed）。<ref>{{Cite news|first=Alex|author=Seitz-Wald|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/democrats-vs-trump/trump-rips-top-democrat-jon-ossoff-georgia-special-election-n747361|title=Trump takes to Twitter to blast leading Dem as 'super Liberal'|work=[[NBC_News|NBC News]]|date=2017-04-17|accessdate=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107185029/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/democrats-vs-trump/trump-rips-top-democrat-jon-ossoff-georgia-special-election-n747361}}</ref>FactCheck.org调查称特朗普的主张是对奥索夫立场的歪曲，没有证据表明奥索夫曾经主张进行任何广泛的加税。<ref name=":5">{{Cite news|first=Robert|author=Farley|first2=Eugene|author2=Kiely|url=http://www.factcheck.org/2017/04/trump-distorts-ossoffs-record/|title=Trump Distorts Ossoff's Record|date=2017-04-18|work=[[FactCheck.org|FactCheck.org]]}}</ref>尽管如此，奥索夫表示，他愿意与特朗普在他们所共同关心的议题上合作，例如[[基础设施|基础设施]]支出方面。[[唐納·川普對俄洩密事件|特朗普向俄罗斯披露]]机密信息后，奥索夫针对弹劾行动说：“我不认为我们到了（弹劾的）程度。” <ref name=":7">{{Cite web|title=Ossoff on Trump impeachment: 'I don't think we're there'|url=https://www.ajc.com/blog/politics/ossoff-trump-impeachment-don-think-there/OLqymNW4d7cYaus054rfiK/|author=Bluestein|date=2017-05-30|first=Greg|work=[[The_Atlanta_Journal-Constitution|The Atlanta Journal-Constitution]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201221153828/https://www.ajc.com/blog/politics/ossoff-trump-impeachment-don-think-there/OLqymNW4d7cYaus054rfiK/|archivedate=2020-12-21|accessdate=2021-01-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>他呼吁“对[[俄羅斯干預2016年美國總統選舉|俄罗斯情报部门在美国大选中的干预程度进行]]全面，透明和独立的评估。国会的监督者以及任何独立顾问或委员会都应遵循事实，不管它们将调查带到哪里。” 

