== 个人生活 ==
奥索夫的母亲希瑟·芬顿（Heather Fenton）是澳大利亚移民，<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/can-this-democrat-win-the-georgia-sixth|title=Can This Democrat Win the Georgia Sixth?|author=Bethea|first=Charles|date=2017-03-03|work=[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]|accessdate=2017-03-08}}</ref>她与别人一起共同创立了新能量（NewPower）[[政治行動委員會|政治行動委員會]]，该组织致力于选举妇女担任[[佐治亚州|佐治亚州]]地方职务。<ref name="Hefty-Advantages-AJC"/><ref name="fenton-ga">{{Cite web|title=Our Team – NewPowerPAC|url=https://newpowerpacga.org/about-us/our-team/|access-date=2021-01-06|archive-date=2021-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210106023335/https://newpowerpacga.org/about-us/our-team/}}</ref>他的父亲理查德·奥索夫（Richard Ossoff）是俄罗斯裔犹太人和立陶宛裔犹太人，是斯特拉福德出版公司（Strafford Publications）的所有者。奥索夫从小依犹太人传统长大。<ref>{{Cite web|title=A Jewish candidate gives Democrats hope in Atlanta's suburbs|url=http://www.jta.org/2017/03/21/news-opinion/politics/a-jewish-candidate-gives-democrats-hope-in-atlantas-suburbs|accessdate=2017-03-28|author=Kampeas|date=2017-03-21|first=Ron|publisher=[[Jewish_Telegraphic_Agency|Jewish Telegraphic Agency]]|archive-date=2018-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180124112424/https://www.jta.org/2017/03/21/news-opinion/politics/a-jewish-candidate-gives-democrats-hope-in-atlantas-suburbs}}</ref>

奥索夫的妻子是[[埃默里大学|埃默里大学]]的[[婦科學|婦科學]]住院医师爱丽舍·克拉玛（Alisha Kramer）。<ref>{{Cite news|author=Moore|first=Elena|title=Georgia Democrat Jon Ossoff Attempts Homebound Political Comeback|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/04/25/843255113/georgia-democrat-jon-ossoff-attempts-homebound-political-comeback|accessdate=2020-06-11|publisher=NPR|date=2020-04-25|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108205635/https://www.npr.org/2020/04/25/843255113/georgia-democrat-jon-ossoff-attempts-homebound-political-comeback}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Our Residents|url=https://med.emory.edu/departments/gynecology-obstetrics/education/residency/our-residents/index.html|accessdate=2020-11-04|work=Gynecology and Obstetrics Residency Program|publisher=Emory University School of Medicine|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108025136/https://med.emory.edu/departments/gynecology-obstetrics/education/residency/our-residents/index.html}}</ref>

